    "name": "BallMan",
    "steam_appid": 3256630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>BallMan</i> is a smiley round creature who likes to spend its days rolling around the world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But suddenly, during the year<i> 1994</i>, something weird happened and several bad creatures called <i>BadBalls</i> appeared, messing up BallMan's life. <i>Make BallMan's world free again!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide it through 7 different levels, such caves, countryside and more, helping it clean up its world while enjoying the awesome old school MIDI soundtrack and the funny animations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself and the other players making the highest score on the scoreboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>real </strong>arcade game where you have to insert coins to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...of course you don't have to actually insert coins into your PC :) Read the control list below for further information.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Default controls:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up arrow -&gt; Climb ladder up, look upwards</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Down arrow -&gt; Climb ladder down, look downwards, crouch</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Left arrow -&gt; Roll to the left</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Right arrow -&gt; Roll to the right</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>N -&gt; Jump</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M -&gt; Fire  </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>C -&gt; Insert coin</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game managing:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>P -&gt; Pause the game</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Esc -&gt; Pause and go windowed mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>0 -&gt; Fullscreen mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1 -&gt; Windowed (small)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 -&gt; Windowed (medium)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 -&gt; Windowed (large) </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Everyone can enjoy BallMan! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why? Because it's only a <strong>few megabytes </strong>in size and you will download it in a couple of seconds! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, you <strong>don't need </strong>a thousand dollars gaming PC to run it, your grandma's old laptop will be more than enough to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...true story, tested by myself ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have fun, and follow me for new releases!</strong></p>",
